      "n": 28,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Jehkabs darrija ta/ un beidse to Meddetu ar to/ tad de-\nwe wiꞥſch tam Raëli/ ſawu Mei-\ntu par Seewu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Lahbans dewe Raëlei/ ſawu Kalponi Bila/ par Kalponi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Jehkabs gahje arri-\ndſan pee Raëles/ un miḣleja to\nRaëli wairak ne ka Leï/ un tas\nKalpoja pee winna wehl zittus ſeptin Gaddns.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS redſeja/\nka Lea eenihdeta tappe/ tad dar-\nrija wiꞥſch to augliga/ bet Raë-\nle bija neaugliga.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Lea tappe gruhta/ un\ndſemdeja Dehlu/ un noẜauze win-\nna Wahrdü Rubbens/ jo ta ſaz-\nzija: Tapehz/ ka tas KUNGS\nmannas Behdas irr ſkattijis/ jo\nnu miḣtohs mann mans Wihrs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ta tappe atkaṫ gruh-\nta/ un dſemdeja Dehlu/ un ſaz-\nzija: Tapehz/ ka tas KUNGS\nDsirdejis/ man eenihdetu eſam /\nirr wiꞥſch man arridsan to de-\nwis/ un noẜauze winna Wahrdü\nSihmeans.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ta tappe atkaṫ gruh-\nta/ un dſemdeja Dehlu/ un ſaz-\nzija: Nu/ ſcho Brihdi mans\nWihrs man peedſihwohs/ jo es\nefinu winnam trihs Dehlus dſem-\ndeji/ tadeht noẜauze ta winna\nWahrdü Lewis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un winna tappe atkaṫ\ngruhta/ un dſemdeja Dehlu/ un\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "arridsan par to Kalposchanu/ jo ſazzija: Scho Brihdi fla-\ntew buhs wehlzittus ſeptin Gad-\ndus pee man kalpohf.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "es to KUNGU/ tadeht ni\nta winna Wahrdü Juhd-\nta mittejahs dſemdeht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Roëleirr ne-augliga: 1. Un doḣd fat-\nni Bila Jehkabam par Seewu:\ndſemde Danu un Nawtalu: 5/7-\narri ſawu Kalponi Silpu Jehlabam\nwu/ ta dſemde Gadu/ Ahseru: 9:\npadarra Rhelu augliga/ ta dſemde\n22. Jehkabs ſaderr ar Lahbanu ta\npoṣhanas pehi: 25.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ad nu Raële redſe-\nta Jehkabam ne ds-\nja/ eenihdeja ta\nMahfu/ un ſazzija ue Jeh-\nDabbu man Behrnus/ bet j\ntad man ja-mirſt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad apſaitahs Jeh-\nus Raëles/ un ſazzija : W-\npar Deeiu efmu/ kas tew ta\nMeefas Augtue leedsis irr?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ta ſazzija: Redſ/ fe-\nmanna Kalpone Bila/eij pee t-\nka ta us mannru Klehpi dſet-\nun es arridsan zaur winnu\nbehrnota tohpu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un winna dewe tam Q-\nfawu Kalponi par Seewu/\nJehkabs gahje pee tahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Bila tappe gruhta/\ndſemdeja Jehkabam Dehlu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad ſazzija Raële: De-\nirr man teesajis/ un arrid-\nmannu Balsi paklaufijis/\nman Dehlu dewis/ tadeht\nfanze ta winna Wahrdü Da-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Bila Raëles Kal-\ntappe atkaṫ gruhta/ un dſem-\nJehkabam to ohtru Dehlu.\n"
    }
  ],
